replyContent: You must wait for Anonify to be connected before being able to use the network. The button will say ON when it is ready, and a notification saying 'Anonify Connected' will appear for a few seconds. This is how it is supposed to work: connections are blocked until ready to prevent leaks. Use the Orxy app to get messages about connection progress.

content: Only one question the Nsa/fbi are able to make their own tor relay nodes which may compromise some data. Is that true with this app?
replyContent: Anyone can run a relay exit node, but Tor is designed to prevent an exit node from tracing a connection back to its origin. Follow the tips and guidelines described here and on the Tor project page to help prevent exit nodes from correlating your data. Use HTTPS/SSL whenever possible.
